                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#17v" facs="122"/>
                    Text written in a circle around a box filled with text. The text in the center reads: “Seventy-two languages given to the human beings.” The text written around the box attempts to list some of the languages, including Hebrew and Italian.  According to the commentary tradition on Genesis 11 and Acts 2, God gave seventy-two languages to the disciples at Pentecost
                    </desc>
                    </item>
